    {
      "id": "performance-audit-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Performance Audit",
      "position": {
        "x": 140,
        "y": -860
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Performance Audit\n\nStabilize large-graph performance so browse mode, authoring, and copy/export stop freezing the browser.\n\nThis graph tracks the concrete remediation work surfaced by the current audit: edge rendering cost, always-on physics churn, history growth, group recomputation, semantic adjacency expansion, and heavy save/export paths."
      }
